				<div class="ls_help_rg_nr">
					<div class="help_bt">a. We offer returns and replacements as well as after-sale repairs within 7 days from the date of delivery marked by Seller in order. You can contact our service personnel for the application of returns, replacements or repairs. Specific standards for returns and replacements as follows:</div>
					<div class="help_nr">
						<p><img src="newcss/css/images/thhzc_en.jpg"/></p>
					</div>
					<div class="help_bt">b. Rule to determine seller-marked delivery date:</div>
					<div class="help_nr">Order delivered by Huika Mall: Subject to the date of delivery marked in order.</div>
					<div class="help_bt">c. For items without any kind of defects or problems, Huika Mall promises:</div>
					<div class="help_nr">As long as the item is not used or altered in any way (in the same condition as it was received), we offer full refund (excluding return shopping costs, which shall be borne by customer) within 7 days from seller-marked delivery date. Sellers in Huika Mall are selling brand-new products, and for the benefit of customers, the following conditions are considered as items being altered:
						<p>1. For phones, cameras and laptops: Original packaging has been opened or batteries have been put on for start-up;</p>
						<p>2. For clothing, shoes and hats: Packaging or tag has been damaged, or item has been washed or worn; </p>
						<p>3. For sealing products: Original packaging has been opened;</p>
						<p>4. Product has been energized, in water or inserted into slot for use;</p>
						<p>5. Return of diamonds, gold, watches, jewelry and accessories is not acceptable;</p>
						<p>6. Return of food, health care products, personal care supplies, intimates, cosmetics, virtual commodities and software is not acceptable;</p>
						<p>7. Product has clear statement of return not supported at the time of purchase;</p>
						<p>8. Other conditions that affect the reselling of products</p>
					</div>
					<div class="help_bt">d. Note: Returns and replacements will not be accepted under the circumstances below: </div>
					<div class="help_nr">1. Product is not sold in Huika Mall (unmatched Serial No.);
						<p>2. Product is out of warranty;</p>
						<p>3. Quality problem is caused by unauthorized maintenance, misuse, collision, negligence, liquid inflow, accident, alteration and incorrect installation, or the tag, machine number and anti-fake label has been torn down or altered; </p>
						<p>4. Original packaging of sealing products has been opened and the disposable sealing label or tape has been damaged (except quality problem); </p>
						<p>5. Product has been used (except quality problem);</p>
						<p>6. Other conditions that returns and replacements does not apply according to law. </p>
					</div>
					<div class="help_bt">e. Supplement</div>
					<div class="help_nr">Once payment succeeded, you can contact Customer Service to apply for refund or return within 7 days from the marked delivery date, otherwise, you will not be able to return an item once the deal is closed. In case of after-sale repairs needed due to quality problem, please apply for after-sale repair service (see Help Center- Return Policy for details) and contact service personnel to settle within 7 days upon close of transaction. Returns and replacements will not be provided 7 days after close of transaction; however, under special circumstance, refund may be promised upon mutual negotiation and the amount of sale price minus intermediate price differentials will be refunded.</div>
					
					
